          <h4>&rarr; Rose asks guest about likes & interests &rarr; Offers to make introductions</h4>
        </div>

        <div class="example">
          <img src="images/flight1.svg" alt="">
          <h3>"Could you help me find a good flight?"</h3>
          <h4>&rarr; Rose asks about desired departure info &rarr; Sends possible flight options</h4>
        </div>
      </div>

