          <h3>“Make sure to RSVP by August 10th for Chris and Jacob’s wedding! Message me if you have any questions :)”</h3>
          <h4>&rarr; You tell Rose to contact guests who haven't RSVP'd &rarr; Rose can collect guest status info</h4>
